      <title>泰国通胀率七个月来首次转正</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/thai-inflation-turns-positive-for-first-time-in-seven-months</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在政府允许石油零售商提高柴油价格以及由于炎热的热浪导致新鲜食品和蔬菜变得更加昂贵之后，泰国的通货膨胀七个月来首次转为正值。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/thai-inflation-turns-positive-for-first-time-in-seven-months</guid>
